  <summary date="2020-04-24T14:04:03Z" status="Introduced in House">Universal Charitable Giving Act of 2019

This bill allows individual taxpayers a deduction from gross income (above-the-line deduction) for charitable contributions even if such taxpayers do not elect to itemize deductions for the taxable year. The deduction may not exceed one-third of the taxpayer's standard deduction amount.</summary>
